<!-- BONUS RULES -->\n        <div class=\"tcs-review-block\">\n          <span class=\"tcs-label-pill\">Bonus Rules</span>\n          <h2>Wagering Requirements &amp; Important Terms</h2>\n          <p>\n            The welcome offer is large, but the terms are still the deciding factor for real-world value. During our review, terms were displayed clearly on promotional pages rather than being hidden behind unclear max-cashout restrictions.\n          </p>\n          <ul>\n            <li><strong>Typical wagering:</strong> around <strong>x45</strong> on bonus funds for the main welcome bonus.</li>\n            <li><strong>Game contribution:</strong> slots typically contribute fully; table and live games may contribute less or be excluded.</li>\n            <li><strong>Bet limits:</strong> maximum bet rules may apply while wagering is active.</li>\n            <li><strong>Time limits:</strong> bonuses and free spins are usually time-limited once activated.</li>\n          </ul>\n          <p class=\"tcs-tagline\">\n            If you plan a large first deposit, check the maximum bet and eligible game list first. These terms have the biggest impact on completion time and bonus conversion.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- GAMES & PROVIDERS -->\n        <div class=\"tcs-review-block\">\n          <span class=\"tcs-label-pill\">Games &amp; Providers</span>\n          <h2>Game Library &amp; Software Providers</h2>\n          <p>\n            Fairspin has a large mixed catalogue covering slots, table games, live dealer titles, instant-win games and a sportsbook. The lobby includes filtering tools to help navigate the volume.\n          </p>\n          <ul>\n            <li><strong>5,000+ games</strong> across slots, table and specialty categories.</li>\n            <li><strong>20+ providers</strong> including major slot brands and live dealer studios.</li>\n            <li><strong>Live casino:</strong> blackjack, roulette, baccarat and game-show formats.</li>\n            <li><strong>Instant-win &amp; crash games</strong> common to crypto-focused platforms.</li>\n            <li><strong>Sportsbook:</strong> pre-match and live markets for major sports and esports.</li>\n          </ul>\n          <p class=\"tcs-tagline\">\n            Game availability can differ by location due to provider restrictions. The most reliable check is the live lobby after login.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- SUPPORT -->\n        <div class=\"tcs-review-block\">\n          <span class=\"tcs-label-pill\">Support</span>\n          <h2>Customer Support &amp; Service Quality</h2>\n          <p>\n            Fairspin performed strongly in our support tests. Live chat response time was fast and agents provided consistent information about promotions, limits and policy questions.\n          </p>\n          <ul>\n            <li>Live chat connected in approximately <strong>5 seconds</strong> during testing.</li>\n            <li>Agents provided <strong>clear answers</strong> about wagering and payment limits.</li>\n            <li>Support acknowledged RG tool limitations during the audit period.</li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- REPUTATION / PLAYER FEEDBACK -->\n        <div class=\"tcs-review-block\">\n          <span class=\"tcs-label-pill\">Reputation</span>\n          <h2>Reputation, Trustpilot &amp; Player Feedback</h2>\n          <p>\n            We incorporate external review signals into the TCS Score using a formula-based approach and review-volume weighting. For offshore casinos, the most important patterns tend to be related to withdrawals, KYC disputes, bonus enforcement, and account restrictions.\n          </p>\n          <p class=\"tcs-tagline\">\n            When comparing similar casinos, prioritise consistent themes over single reviews. A pattern of payout delays or unclear bonus enforcement carries more weight than isolated complaints.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n\n      </div>\n\n      <