ensing in many cases.\n          </p>\n          <p>\n            The website uses HTTPS encryption and provides published privacy and KYC policies. Players should still treat offshore regulation as meaningfully different from local Tier-1 coverage, especially for disputes and complaint escalation.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- PLAYER PROTECTION / RESPONSIBLE GAMBLING -->\n        <div class=\"tcs-review-block\">\n          <span class=\"tcs-label-pill\">Responsible Gambling</span>\n          <h2>Responsible Gambling Tools</h2>\n          <p>\n            Responsible gambling tools are a key evaluation point. During our audit, Fairspin\u2019s in-account tools were described as limited or undergoing updates, which reduced its score in player protection despite strong performance elsewhere.\n          </p>\n          <ul>\n            <li>In-account limits and exclusions were <strong>not fully available</strong> during our audit window.</li>\n            <li>Players were advised to use <strong>banking or wallet limits</strong> to control spend.</li>\n            <li>Support was able to explain the current tool status transparently.</li>\n          </ul>\n          <p class=\"tcs-tagline\">\n            If you rely on strict deposit limits, time-outs or self-exclusion controls, prioritise casinos with fully integrated RG settings under Tier-1 regulation.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- MOBILE -->\n        <div class=\"tcs-review-block\">\n          <span class=\"tcs-label-pill\">Mobile</span>\n          <h2>Mobile Experience &amp; User Interface</h2>\n          <p>\n            The Fairspin website is responsive and functions well on modern mobile browsers. Navigation is designed around search, filters and game tags, which helps on smaller screens.\n          </p>\n          <ul>\n            <li>Responsive layout for iOS and Android browsers.</li>\n            <li>Stable performance across slots, live casino and sportsbook.</li>\n    